description: Law enforcement in the small town of Buckner, Mo., is the focus of this docudrama executive-produced by Bischoff Hervey Entertainment ("The Devils Ride," "Hardcore Pawn: Chicago"). Viewers ride along as a street crew continually clashes with the cops sworn to bring them down. Chief of Police Mike Cook and his brother Steve, who heads Buckner's Criminal Task Force, suspect that siblings John and Josh Monk are responsible for a surge in crime, and the bad blood threatens a good town. Complete access to the police force and the "outlaws" presents an unblemished view from both sides of the law
